title: Looking for ranked team members, Gold 2+, Must be on very often & have TS.

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
Anyone that wants to join add me in game ( Plat5+ ). Just because i add you will not mean your on the team. I'm also looking for a people that have good game knowledge.

Ts is a must, if i do manage to get this team together and working it wont really be a piss farty around team I'm looking to actually get somewhere in this game with this team, I've never really got past bronze with a team because people never get back on after the first night, If this happens with this team i will kick who ever and replace them until we can get a solid team together.

Top: NTF
Mid: Kat To Plat
